\c 26
\s Ukubusa kukaUziya
\p
\v 1 Bonke abantu bakoJuda basebethatha uUziya owayeleminyaka elitshumi lesithupha, bambeka waba yinkosi esikhundleni sikayise uAmaziya.
\v 2 Yena wakha iElothi, wayibuyisela koJuda emva kokulala kwenkosi laboyise.
\v 3 U-Uziya wayeleminyaka elitshumi lesithupha lapho esiba yinkosi; wabusa iminyaka engamatshumi amahlanu lambili eJerusalema\x + 2 Kho. 15.2,3.\x*. Lebizo likanina lalinguJekoliya weJerusalema.
\v 4 Wasesenza okuqondileyo emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd* njengakho konke uAmaziya uyise ayekwenzile\x + 2 Kho. 15.2,3.\x*.
\v 5 Njalo wayemdinga uNkulunkulu ensukwini zikaZekhariya\x + 24.2.\x* owayelokuqedisisa emibonweni kaNkulunkulu; langezinsuku zokudinga kwakhe iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu wamphumelelisa\x + Dan. 1.17. 10.1.\x*.
\v 6 Wasephuma walwa lamaFilisti\x + Isa. 14.29.\x*, wadilizela phansi umduli weGathi\x + 1 Sam. 17.4.\x* lomduli weJabine\x + Josh. 15.11.\x* lomduli weAshidodi\x + 1 Sam. 5.1.\x*, wakha imizi eAshidodi laphakathi kwamaFilisti.
\v 7 UNkulunkulu wasemsiza ukumelana lamaFilisti\x + 21.16.\x*, lokumelana lamaArabhiya ayehlala eGuri-Bhali\x + 21.16.\x*, lamaMewuni\x + 20.1. Hlu. 10.12.\x*.
\v 8 AmaAmoni\x + 1 Sam. 11.1.\x* asesipha umthelo kuUziya\x + 17.11. 2 Sam. 8.2.\x*, lebizo lakhe lahamba laze lafika engenelweni leGibhithe, ngoba waziqinisa waze waba sengqongeni.
\v 9 Futhi uUziya wakha imiphotshongo eJerusalema esangweni lengonsi\x + 2 Kho. 14.13.\x* lesangweni lesigodi\x + Neh. 2.13,15. 3.13.\x* lengonsini, wayiqinisa\x + Neh. 3.19.\x*.
\v 10 Wakha lemiphotshongo enkangala, wagebha imithombo eminengi, ngoba wayelenkomo ezinengi esihotsheni kanye lemagcekeni\x + Dute. 3.10.\x*, abalimi\x + Jow. 1.11.\x* lezisebenzi zezivini ezintabeni\x + Jow. 1.11.\x* leKharmeli\x + Josh. 15.55.\x*, ngoba wayengothanda umhlabathi.
\v 11 Futhi uUziya wayelebutho elilwayo eliphuma impi ngamaviyo\x + 2 Kho. 6.23.\x* ngokwenani lokubalwa kwabo ngesandla sikaJeyiyeli umabhalane loMahaseya umbusi phansi kwesandla sikaHananiya, \add omunye\add* wezinduna zenkosi\x + 1 Lan. 23.4. Nani 11.16.\x*.
\v 12 Inani lonke lezinhloko zaboyise lamaqhawe alamandla lalizinkulungwane ezimbili lamakhulu ayisithupha.
\v 13 Laphansi kwesandla sazo kwakulamandla ebutho elizinkulungwane ezingamakhulu amathathu lesikhombisa lamakhulu amahlanu elalisilwa ngamandla obuqhawe ukusiza inkosi limelene lesitha\x + 25.5.\x*.
\v 14 U-Uziya wasebalungisela, ibutho lonke, izihlangu\x + Neh. 4.13,16.\x* lemikhonto\x + Neh. 4.13,16.\x* lamakhowa\x + 1 Sam. 17.5,38.\x* lamabhatshi ensimbi\x + Neh. 4.16. Jobe 41.26. Eks. 28.32. 39.23.\x*\x + 1 Sam. 17.5,38.\x* lamadandili lamatshe ezavutha\x + Neh. 4.13,16.\x*.
\v 15 EJerusalema wasesenza imitshina, eyaqanjwa ngohlakaniphileyo\x + Tshu. 7.29. Tshu. 7.25,27. 9.10.\x*, ukuthi ibe phezu kwemiphotshongo laphezu kwezingonsi ukuphosa ngemitshoko langamatshe amakhulu. Lebizo lakhe laphuma laze laba khatshana, ngoba wasizwa ngokumangalisayo waze waqina\x + Zaga 21.9. 25.24.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Kodwa eseqinile\x + 12.1. 25.3. Dute. 32.15.\x*, inhliziyo yakhe yaziphakamisela encithakalweni. Ngoba waphambuka eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wakhe\x + 25.19. 32.25. Hez. 28.2,5,17. Dute. 8.14. 2 Kho. 14.10. Hab. 2.4.\x*, wasengena ethempelini leN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Eks. 40.5.\x* ukuze atshise impepha\x + 2 Kho. 16.12,13.\x* phezu kwelathi lempepha\x + Eks. 40.5.\x*.
\v 17 UAzariya umpristi wasengena emva kwakhe elabapristi beN\nd kosi\nd* abangamatshumi ayisificaminwembili\x + 1 Lan. 6.10.\x*, amadoda alamandla\x + 28.6. 2 Kho. 2.16.\x*.
\v 18 Basebemelana loUziya inkosi, bathi kuye: Kakusikho okwakho, Uziya, ukutshisela iN\nd kosi\nd* impepha\x + Nani 16.40. 18.7.\x*, kodwa ngokwabapristi, amadodana kaAroni abehlukaniselwe ukutshisa impepha. Phuma endaweni engcwele, ngoba uphambukile; njalo kakusikho kodumo lwakho oluvela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu\x + Eks. 30.7,8.\x*.
\v 19 Wasethukuthela uUziya, njalo kwakulodengezi esandleni sakhe ukuze atshise impepha; esebathukuthelele abapristi, kwabonakala ubulephero ebunzini lakhe phambi kwabapristi endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd*, ngaphezu kwelathi lempepha\x + Eks. 4.6.\x*.
\v 20 UAzariya umpristi oyinhloko labo bonke abapristi basebemkhangela, khangela-ke, wayelobulephero ebunzini lakhe; basebemkhupha lapho masinyane\x + Esta 6.14.\x*, yebo laye uqobo waphangisa ukuphuma\x + Esta 6.12. Esta 3.15.8.14.\x*, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* yayimtshayile\x + 2 Kho. 15.5-7.\x*.
\v 21 U-Uziya inkosi waba ngumlephero kwaze kwaba lusuku lokufa kwakhe; wahlala endlini eyehlukanisiweyo engumlephero, ngoba waqunywa wasuka endlini kaJehova. Njalo uJothamu indodana yakhe wayephezu kwendlu yenkosi, esahlulela abantu belizwe.
\p
\v 22 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaUziya, ezokuqala lezokucina\x + 1 Lan. 29.29.\x*, uIsaya umprofethi, indodana kaAmozi, wazibhala\x + Isa. 1.1. 6.1.\x*.
\v 23 U-Uziya waselala laboyise; basebemngcwaba kuboyise ensimini yokungcwaba eyayingeyamakhosi, ngoba bathi: Ungumlephero. UJothamu indodana yakhe wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe\x + 2 Kho. 21.18,26.\x*.